data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 1.75-bath home nestled against majestic mountain views! The inviting front porch sets a serene tone as you approach, beckoning you inside. The living room captivates with its soothing palette and plush carpeting, making it an ideal spot to unwind. The eat-in kitchen boasts ample counter space, paneled cabinets, matching appliances, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar to ensure that meal preparations are a delight. The cozy main bedroom is a tranquil retreat with a private bathroom that promises relaxation. Outside, the backyard showcases a covered patio for alfresco dining and ample room for hosting gatherings while enjoying picturesque views. Come and experience it for yourself!
